*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Build results
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
bin/
obj/
Debug/
Release/

## Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons
.vs/
*.vsp
*.vspx
*.cache
*.log

## Visual Studio Code workspace settings
.vscode/

## NuGet
packages/
*.nupkg
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

